<meta name="assert" content="oklab() with no alpha">
<style>
    .test { background-color: red; width: 12em; height: 12em; }
    .test { background-color: oklab(51.975% -0.1403 0.0); } /* green (sRGB #008000) converted to OKLab */
</style>
<body>
    <p><p><p><p>Test passes if you see a green square, and no red.</p></p></p></p>
